OL,3,CLucy Letby inquiry should be
OL,4,Clivestreamed to stop 'distressing'
OL,5,Cconspiracies
OL,7,FAn inquiry into killer nurse Lucy
OL,8,FLetby should be livestreamed to
OL,9,Fprevent the spread of "grossly
OL,10,Foffensive" conspiracy theories,
OL,11,Flawyers for her victim's families have
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FThe inquiry will look into how the
OL,15,Fnurse was able to murder babies on the
OL,16,FCountess of Chester's neonatal unit in
OL,17,F2015 and 2016, as well as the conduct
OL,18,Fof others at the hospital and the
OL,19,Fculture in the NHS as a whole.
