OL,7,FA preliminary hearing for the inquiry,
OL,8,Fchaired by Lady Justice Thirlwall, was
OL,9,Fheld at Chester Racecourse when
OL,10,Fsubmissions on whether the hearings
OL,11,Fshould be publicly broadcast were
OL,12,Fheard.
OL,14,FPeter Skelton KC, representing
OL,15,Ffamilies of six babies, said Letby's
OL,16,Fcrimes continued to be the subject of
OL,17,Fconspiracy theories online.
