OL,4,Clivestreamed to stop 'distressing'
OL,5,Cconspiracies
OL,7,FHe described the theories as "grossly
OL,8,Foffensive" and "distressing" for the
OL,9,Ffamilies, who he compared to relatives
OL,10,Fof US school shooting victims.
OL,12,FHe added: "One of the most effective
OL,13,Fantidotes to those theories and the
OL,14,Fdamage they cause will be to see and
OL,15,Fto hear the people involved in the
OL,16,Fhospital give a true and comprehensive
OL,17,Faccount of the facts."
