OL,4,Clivestreamed to stop 'distressing'
OL,5,Cconspiracies
OL,7,FHe said a submission by lawyers
OL,8,Frepresenting the hospital, which said
OL,9,Fa livestream might make witnesses less
OL,10,Finclined to speak with candour, was
OL,11,F"extraordinary".
OL,13,FHe said: "All the staff working at the
OL,14,Fhospital are public servants, they
OL,15,Fhave a moral obligation to give a true
OL,16,Fand complete account."
OL,18,FThe inquiry will have powers to compel
OL,19,Fwitnesses to give evidence.
