OL,7,FRichard Baker KC, representing some of
OL,8,Fthe other families, said his clients
OL,9,Fhad suffered "an unimaginable harm in
OL,10,Funimaginable circumstances".
OL,12,FHe said: "Their desire in this case is
OL,13,Ffor change and so that others do not
OL,14,Fexperience what they have experienced."
OL,16,FBut, he said, they were "saddened" and
OL,17,F"concerned" at the suggestion the lack
OL,18,Fof transparency might continue.
