OL,7,FAndrew Kennedy KC, representing the
OL,8,FCountess of Chester, said the hospital
OL,9,Fwanted to provide "as much assistance"
OL,10,Fto the inquiry as it could.
OL,12,FBut, he said there was a "high level
OL,13,Fof anxiety" from staff at the prospect
OL,14,Fof giving evidence which was
OL,15,Flivestreamed.
OL,17,FHe said: "Our desire, and no doubt the
OL,18,Finquiry's desire, is for witnesses to
OL,19,Fbe able to speak frankly and with
OL,20,Fcandour and anything that can be done
OL,21,Fto facilitate that should be done.
