OL,7,F"If a witness is concerned about
OL,8,Flivestreaming then if we can remove
OL,9,Fthat concern we can, we would suggest,
OL,10,Fencourage candour, frankness and
OL,11,Fopenness."
OL,13,FRachel Langdale KC, counsel to the
OL,14,Finquiry, said court orders that
OL,15,Fprevent the identification of a number
OL,16,Fof people involved, including all of
OL,17,Fthe babies, had to be complied with.
