OL,7,FLady Justice Thirlwall said she would
OL,8,Fgive her decision on whether the
OL,9,Fhearings would be broadcast at a later
OL,10,Fdate.
OL,12,FShe started the proceedings, which
OL,13,Flasted just over an hour and a half,
OL,14,Fwith a pause for reflection for the
OL,15,F"lives lost", "injuries sustained" and
OL,16,F"suffering" of the families.
