OL,7,FThe hearing was told 188 requests for
OL,8,Finformation had been made to
OL,9,Findividuals including midwives,
OL,10,Fnurses, doctors, managers and members
OL,11,Fof the hospital board.
OL,13,FMs Langdale said detailed questions
OL,14,Fhad been asked about involvement in
OL,15,Fthe care of particular babies,
OL,16,Fsuspicions and concerns about Letby,
OL,17,Fmortality rates and other issues.
OL,19,FShe added: "Questions are asked about
OL,20,Fwhy suspicions were not reported to
OL,21,Fpolice sooner."
